</h2>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Redband Trout</strong>: Native to tailwaters like the Crooked below Bowman Dam
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Rainbow Trout</strong>: Stocked and wild—found in reservoirs and rivers.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Brown Trout</strong>: Catch-and-release opportunities at East Lake and Crane Prairie .
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Brook Trout &amp; Cutthroat</strong>: High-country gems in lakes like Hosmer and Sparks
    </li>
</ul>
